---
title: Super Green Stir-Fry (v) with Roasted Broccoli, Ginger Peanut Dressing
description: This super green stir-fry is the perfect quick-fix recipe if you’re craving something fresh and flavourful. Crunchy green vegetables like beans and broccoli pick up all the flavours in the peanutty sauce, whilst fresh herbs and lime juice keep things fresh. Wholesome, hearty and packed with nourishing ingredients, make this your dinnertime go-to.
